    <h1>Chocolate Cake Recipe</h1>
    <hr>

    <img src="Chocolate cake.jpg" alt="Chocolate Cake " width="250">

    <p>This is a quick and delicious chocolate cake recipe.
        That can be made in just 5 minutes. Perfect for sudden sweet
        cravings
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2> Cooking Details</h2>
    <p><strong>Preparation Time:</strong>2 minutes</p>
    <p><strong>Cooking Time:</strong>3 minutes</p>
    <p><strong>Servings:</strong>1 person</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>4 tablespoons flour</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons cocoa powder</li>
        <li>3 tablespoon milk</li>
        <li>2 tablespoon sugar</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons oil</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Preparation Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Mix all the Ingredients well in a mug</li>
        <li>Add milk and oil, then mix well</li>
        <li>Microwave for 3 minutes</li>
        <li> Let it cool slightly before eating</li>
        <li> Enjoy your Chocolate Mug cake!!!</li>
    </ol>
</body>
